# Praxo-Picos Global Cursor Rules

Project: praxo-picos
Default risk tier: 1

- Always use the Task Packet format in `.cursor/prompts/task-packet.md`.
- Prefer small diffs and composable refactors.
- Emit or update unit tests for any behavior changes.
- All webhook handlers:
  - must return quickly (no network calls inline)
  - must verify signatures before processing
- Never include secrets in code, logs, prompts, or PRs.
- Every change must reference the project_key `praxo-picos` in its task packet.
- Default risk tier is 1; escalate if actual risk is higher.
